clear
color blue
*say 0 ###### More on Sisquo TripleGold networks ######
color black
*say 0 The Sisquo TripleGold network is a state of the art network package using technologies
*say 0 at the pinacle of networking. This radio based network offers speeds of 170 gbps which
*say 0 is far higher than all other radio based network. It also offers a brand new security
*say 0 system called RedBack which integrates itself within normal packets thus avoiding the
*say 0 need for the infamously buggy "packet security". Thus you have a network that offers
*say 0 all the advantages of a radio based network except without the typical low speeds
*say 0 and a network that won't crash every hour.
