@history
clear
color blue
*say ###### Company History ######
color black
*say 0 Established in 2009 following Laura Palmer finishing college and putting forward a proposal
*say 0 for a company to her parents Palmer file hosting has expanded hugely over the past 3 years.
*say 0 Initially the company was simply Laura doing the tech work, her father Leland as accountant
*say 0 and her mother Sarah as joint CEO and publicist. Using a customised version of the 
*say 0 standard filehosting software the company was almost immediately recognised for quality
*say 0 of service and reliability.
*say 0 The company has grown and grown but the family values remained the same aside from when Leland
*say 0 was imprisoned for 37 cases of armed robbery that company has done well. Laura is infact the 
*say 0 only Palmer still in the company as her mother chose to return to her maiden name following
*say 0 the divorce.
*say 0 In 2011 work was finished on a homemade filehosting program written by Laura. Once released
*say 0 it caught on and the money made from selling the software allowed the company to expand even
*say 0 further. The initial program was very basic which made it popular as it provided for every
*say 0 need without being complex. We are currently using a new version of the software which
*say 0 has only just been released however looks set to be better than the previous version in almost
*say 0 every way.
color red
*say Press a key to go back
pause
